    {"type":"text","id":"hyp_c","x":18,"y":214,"width":404,"height":44,"text":"RQ: pregunta abierta exploratoria — \"¿Cómo afectan las restricciones gramaticales a...?\"\nHipótesis: afirmación falseable — H₀: μ_restricciones = μ_baseline  vs  H₁: μ_restricciones > μ_baseline","originalText":"RQ: pregunta abierta exploratoria — \"¿Cómo afectan las restricciones gramaticales a...?\"\nHipótesis: afirmación falseable — H₀: μ_restricciones = μ_baseline  vs  H₁: μ_restricciones > μ_baseline","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#065f46","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":1221,"version":1,"versionNonce":1222,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

